## Additional Notes

If you use notification groups containing **both iOS and Android devices**, some features (such as Android channels and notification grouping)
may not work consistently.

See the official documentation for details:
[Companion App Notification Docs](https://companion.home-assistant.io/docs/notifications/notifications-basic#sending-notifications-to-multiple-devices)

